2. **Check Inventory**: After gathering, I will check my inventory to confirm the amount of copper ore collected.
3. **Plan for Crafting**: Once I have enough copper ore, I can smelt it into copper plates and then craft the electronic circuits needed for the assembling machine.

- Verify the inventory after harvesting to assess how much copper ore I have collected.
